OL,6,FTwo men have been found guilty of the
OL,7,Fmanslaughter of a 71-year-old woman
OL,8,Fwho was left to waste away and die in
OL,9,Fsqualid conditions.
OL,11,FDorothy Morgan weighed just four-and-a-
OL,12,Fhalf-stone when she died at the hands
OL,13,Fof her husband and son.
OL,15,FThe prosecution called it "one of the
OL,16,Fworst cases of gross negligence" she'd
OL,17,Fever seen.
