OL,3,CTwo men found guilty of manslaughter
OL,4,Cof wife and mother
OL,6,FHusband Robert Christopher Morgan, 61,
OL,7,Fand David Holyrood, 53, - Mrs Morgan's
OL,8,Fson from another relationship - were
OL,9,Ffound guilty of manslaughter by a
OL,10,Fmajority of 10 to two at Carlisle
OL,11,FCrown Court.
OL,13,FThe jury sat through weeks of
OL,14,Fharrowing evidence, hearing how the
OL,15,Fpair, who should've cared for her,
OL,16,Fwatched as she wasted away and died.
OL,18,FThey heard evidence that the pensioner
OL,19,Fwas so weak she was unable to move
OL,20,Fbefore either called for help.
