OL,6,FWhen she was finally admitted to the ,
OL,7,FMrs Morgan was found to be suffering
OL,8,Ffrom acute kidney failure, as a result
OL,9,Fof extreme dehydration, and sepsis.
OL,11,FShe died 10 days later, on 4th
OL,12,FFebruary, 2021.
OL,14,F"I should've done more"
OL,16,FWhen Mr Morgan eventually called for
OL,17,Fhelp, he claimed his wife had
OL,18,F"literally tried to starve herself to
OL,19,Fdeath" over several weeks and, he
OL,20,Fobserved, "looks like something from a
OL,21,Fdeath camp."
