OL,6,FSecurity manager, Morgan, said he
OL,7,Fbelieved his wife wouldn't have
OL,8,Faccepted help had it been offered
OL,9,Fsooner, and that "she intended to end
OL,10,Fher life".
OL,12,FBoth men had previously denied charges
OL,13,Fof manslaughter by gross negligence
OL,14,Ffollowing the death of the 71-year-old.
OL,16,FThe verdicts followed deliberations of
OL,17,F23 hours and 12 minutes by jurors.
OL,19,FMorgan closed his eyes as he was found
OL,20,Fguilty, while Holyoak bowed his head
OL,21,Fin the dock as he was convicted.
